OL,3,CMultiple roads closed after serious
OL,4,Ccar crash
OL,6,F11 roads have been closed following a
OL,7,Fserious crash.
OL,9,FMerseyside Police said a car crashed
OL,10,Finto a lamppost on Liverpool Road in
OL,11,FHuyton just before 2am on Friday, 24
OL,12,FJuly.
OL,14,FEmergency services are on the scene
OL,15,Ffollowing the crash, which officers
OL,16,Fsaid involved a black Cupra.
