OL,3,CMultiple roads closed after serious
OL,4,Ccar crash
OL,6,FThe road closures are on Shellingford
OL,7,FRoad, East Prescot Road, Liverpool
OL,8,FRoad, Somerset Road, Back Dovecot
OL,9,FPlace, Dovecot Place, Taurus Road,
OL,10,FTurriff Road, Dinas Lane, Lordens Road
OL,11,Fand Fincham Road.
OL,13,FPeople have been asked to stay away
OL,14,Ffrom the area.
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
